{"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"scalesWithViewingDistance","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and the map is tilted, the annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view appears smaller if it is towards the top of the view (closer to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"horizon) and larger if it is towards the bottom of the view (closer to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"viewpoint). This is also the behavior of ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","type":"reference"},{"text":" objects. When the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or the map’s pitch is zero, the annotation view","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"remains the same size regardless of its position on-screen.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":". Keep this property set to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":" if"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the view’s legibility is important."}]},{"style":"note","name":"Note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Scaling many on-screen annotation views can contribute to poor map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"performance. Consider keeping this property disabled if your use case"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"involves hundreds or thousands of annotation views."}]}]}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view grows and shrinks","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as the distance between the viewpoint and the annotation view changes on a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tilted map.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/scalesWithViewingDistance"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","title":"scalesWithViewingDistance","roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"scalesWithViewingDistance","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L180","fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h"},"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"scalesWithViewingDistance"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)scalesWithViewingDistance"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","title":"MLNAnnotationView","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","isActive":true},{"text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object that corresponds to the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/scalesWithViewingDistance":{"fragments":[{"text":"scalesWithViewingDistance","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/scalesWithViewingDistance","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view grows and shrinks","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as the distance between the viewpoint and the annotation view changes on a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tilted map.","type":"text"}],"title":"scalesWithViewingDistance","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","title":"MLNAnnotationImage","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationImage"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap "},{"code":"UIImage","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by the map view."}],"role":"symbol"}}}